item.title: Something i remember
item.dc:creator: @davidude36 Brolapse
item.description:
@davidude36 wrote:

i was in the first sort of one i believe, we had a few parties then everyone started fighting over which clan is better.
It would have been better if they put the aruguing aside and worked together, though it didn’t happen, so i stopped going to any events lol.

I found it mostly fun because i gave out quite a lot in the few drop parties we had and it felt really good to give it away.
Though I wouldn’t join another clan because I don’t play runescape more than 5 minutes a week.
